exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/09\/surat-al-fatihah-wajib\/","url_meta":{"origin":4288,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Reciting Al-Fatihah in prayer is obligatory","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 9, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA prayer performed by one who has not recited 'the foundation of the Quran' during it is deficient, deficient, deficient, incomplete.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 395 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3087,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/28\/surah-al-fatihah-every-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":4288,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recitation of Surat al-Fatihah in every prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no prayer for one who does not recite the opening of the Book, Surat al-Fatihah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 756, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 394 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28132,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/nawafil-witr-sunan-fajr\/","url_meta":{"origin":4288,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Praying Witr prayer, Sunan of dawn prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray at night, two by two, and make it odd with one cycle. The Prophet would pray two cycles before the morning prayer, so lightly as if the call to prayer were in his ears. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12935,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/sunan-prayers-dhuhur-fajr\/","url_meta":{"origin":4288,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Sunan of Dhuhur and Fajr prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would never miss four cycles before noon prayer and two cycles before dawn prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1182 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0